'''撒拉艾爾'''（[[英語|英語]]：{{lang|en|'''Sabrael'''}}）是於《{{tsl|en|Testament of Solomon|所羅門遺訓}}》和《[[以諾書|以諾三書]]》中被提及的一位[[天使|天使]]。<ref>"Sabrael," in ''A Dictionary of Angels: including the fallen angels'', by {{tsl|en|Gustav Davidson|古斯塔夫·戴維森|Gustav Davidson}}, Simon & Schuster, 1967, p. 252</ref>

在《{{tsl|en|Testament of Solomon|所羅門遺訓}}》中，與別處不同的是，[[烏列爾|烏列爾]]在此書中被列為第三大天使，而撒拉艾爾則被列為第四大天使。<ref name="google.com">{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vZQhBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA77&lpg=PA77&dq=%22Christian+Gnostics%22+by+Gregory+the+Great&source=bl&ots=EaQ2trNlMg&sig=4Er-oDiPSxvDlpznkpQcLjUq1TA&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0CB4Q6AEwAGoVChMIgqmU5J_kxwIVDKCACh19dQdq#v=onepage&q=%22Christian%20Gnostics%22%20by%20Gregory%20the%20Great&f=false|title=The Esoteric Codex: Book of Enoch|work=google.com|access-date=2016-01-23|archive-date=2019-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607181213/https://books.google.com/books?id=vZQhBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA77&lpg=PA77&dq=%22Christian+Gnostics%22+by+Gregory+the+Great&source=bl&ots=EaQ2trNlMg&sig=4Er-oDiPSxvDlpznkpQcLjUq1TA&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0CB4Q6AEwAGoVChMIgqmU5J_kxwIVDKCACh19dQdq#v=onepage&q=%22Christian%20Gnostics%22%20by%20Gregory%20the%20Great&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>

